<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Highness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Highness,</orth> a title of honour given to kings and queens: <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.172" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.127.172" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 127</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.127.172" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 127</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.391" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 391</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.79" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 5, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.122" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.3.76" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 3, 76</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.4.9" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.117" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 117</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.1.42" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 42</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.5.26" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.93" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.56" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.69" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.61" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.4.93" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 4, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 3, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 79</bibl>. 175 etc. Given to other sovereign princes: <bibl n="shak. mm 5.520" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 520</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.520" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 520</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 5.211" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 211</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.292" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 292</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.43" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 54</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 54</bibl> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.1.13" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 13</bibl>. Used, as it seems, in flattery, to address other persons of royal blood: <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.3.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 3, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.13" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 6, 13</bibl>.
